summary: I am currently studying again at Fontys and doing a technical study in mechatronics which is entirely different from my past experiences , of which I have numerous . For 2 Years I was a tour guide in South Africa in the Kwa-Zulu Natal province after which I traveled to Australia to work on a Apiary as a beekeeper, I stayed for 8 months then went back to South africa and again became a tour guide in same region. I stayed In south africa another year after which i moved abroad again this time to the Netherlands.
